### Equipment
A new set of equipment will be added to BP Works shop every patch, until the end of the BP season.

### BP Works Vintage
When BP season ends, the equipment will be moved to a separate shop called **BP Works Vintage** shop for **ONE PATCH**. Here, you get one last chance to purchase the equipment.
- In Vintage shop, you can also convert the new crystallum to the previous crystallum one last time, in case you are short a few crystallum to get an equipment.
